author: AAA3A
name: EmbassyTool
install_msg:
Thank you for installing this cog! 
Do `[p]help` to get the list of commands and their description. 
It does not use user data.
short: A cog to manage a embassy system!
description: Have you ever wanted to set up an embassy system, with many options for the user and the FA team, on your server? Then this cog is for you! It has many settings, buttons, a reaction to create the embassy, many commands working in the embassy channel, different roles with access to different options...
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
